        <section class="max">
            <p class="text-xl text-primary"> &emsp; &emsp;Weblox is a drag-and-drop webpage builder that allows users to
                create and export website code. It utilizes
                the latest technology, Tailwind CSS, a utility-first CSS framework that provides classes that can be
                composed to build any design, directly in your markup. With Weblox, users can create a website without
                needing to write any code, making it accessible for those without a technical background. The generated
                code
                can then be exported for use in other projects or for further customization</p>

