            </p>

            <h4>Styles</h4>
            <p> &emsp;This is the section in which the selected component styles can be changed</p>

            <h4>Trait</h4>
            <p> &emsp;A common use of traits is to customize element attributes (eg. placeholder for input tag) or you
                can also
                bind them to the properties of your components and react to their changes</p>
